00:00:19.980 --> 00:00:24.600
-You know, when we're
writing, it's just

00:00:24.600 --> 00:00:26.820
like working with
another writer,

00:00:26.820 --> 00:00:28.900
and a writer that
I admire, respect.

00:00:28.900 --> 00:00:32.189
