with two collaborators

00:00:32.189 --> 00:00:36.510
in which most of the time
you agree and work very fast,

00:00:36.510 --> 00:00:39.650
and sometimes you fight a lot.

00:00:39.650 --> 00:00:42.100
But it was not unlike
the relationship

00:00:42.100 --> 00:00:44.010
with any other writer.

00:00:44.010 --> 00:00:46.530
Here the plus is that I
got to spend time with him.

