-Not when we're writing.

00:00:50.610 --> 00:00:51.170
-No?

00:00:51.170 --> 00:00:51.680
-No.

00:00:51.680 --> 00:00:54.600
When we're writing, it's like
a complete different thing.

00:00:54.600 --> 00:00:56.890
You're just two writers
working together.

00:00:56.890 --> 00:01:01.040
-This movie, it has a
very difficult topic,

00:01:01.040 --> 00:01:04.099
and you had to face so
many challenges to do it.

00:01:04.099 --> 00:01:06.110
Why did you face all
those challenges?

00:01:06.110 --> 00:01:07.590
Why did you do it?

00:01:07.590 --> 00:01:09.085
-Well, when we
did the script, we

00:01:09.085 --> 00:01:11.220
didn't know it was going
to be so difficult.

00:01:11.220 --> 00:01:13.220
And it was not until we
tried to put it together

00:01:13.220 --> 00:01:15.920
that we realized it
was very difficult.

00:01:15.920 --> 00:01:19.940
And we have to invent our
own technology to do it.

00:01:19.940 --> 00:01:22.530
And so, in many ways, the
journey of making the film

00:01:22.530 --> 00:01:26.930
was very similar to the journey
of our character in the film.

00:01:26.930 --> 00:01:31.120
Because it was a journey
full of adversities.

00:01:31.120 --> 00:01:34.130
When we face a new adversity,
we used to call it OK,

00:01:34.130 --> 00:01:37.210
there's a new shower of debris.

00:01:37.210 --> 00:01:41.080
-So it took you 4 and 1/2
years to do this movie, right?

00:01:41.080 --> 00:01:41.660
-Yeah.

00:01:41.660 --> 00:01:43.750
-And now that it's
done, how do you feel?

00:01:43.750 --> 00:01:44.870
Do you feel relieved?

00:01:44.870 --> 00:01:46.710
-Relieved is the word.

00:01:46.710 --> 00:01:49.260
That's exactly the word.

00:01:49.260 --> 00:01:54.080
You know, when the dogs
are chasing the fox

00:01:54.080 --> 00:01:59.370
and the fox finally gets away,
is the fox happy or relieved?

00:01:59.370 --> 00:02:00.420
I think it's relieved.

00:02:00.420 --> 00:02:02.170
The fox is happy when
he's just frolicking

00:02:02.170 --> 00:02:06.760
in the river with the other
fox and the other puppies.

00:02:06.760 --> 00:02:11.420
But when he's just escaped from
the hounds, he's just relieved.

