00:02:19.370 --> 00:02:20.860
-Every single day.

00:02:20.860 --> 00:02:21.826
-You do?

00:02:21.826 --> 00:02:22.698
-No. [LAUGHS]

00:02:22.698 --> 00:02:24.010
-OK.

