Of course, like everybody, we go
through some periods of despair

00:02:33.530 --> 00:02:37.380
in which you feel not
unlike Ryan that you're

00:02:37.380 --> 00:02:40.210
floating into the void.

00:02:40.210 --> 00:02:44.280
