00:03:08.726 --> 00:03:10.100
-I think it's the
same thing that

00:03:10.100 --> 00:03:13.160
keeps going Ryan
Stone in the film.

00:03:13.160 --> 00:03:14.855
That even if she's
in complete despair,

00:03:14.855 --> 00:03:18.580
there's an impulse that
is even stronger-- that

00:03:18.580 --> 00:03:21.050
is that impulse of life.

00:03:21.050 --> 00:03:23.810
And that impulse is what
I think keeps me going.

00:03:23.810 --> 00:03:26.850
But I think it's the impulse
that keeps everybody going.

